YAY! i'm so happy! last night i went to the airport to meet my aunt and uncle with their new adopted son from russia! i was so excited! so i got out of work and hour and 45 min early so we'd be on time for their flight to arrive. well we got there at 6:30ish and well their plane was supposed to be there at 7:22 well we were all ready when all the passengers from that flight came out of the terminal..they didn't. we waited a while longer thinking that they were just taking their time. well they weren't. we found out that they missed their flight. we all start freaking out.. they were coming in from atlanta by the way..so it was only an hour and 45 min flight..well the next plane was to take off at 8:17 and wouldn't arrive here until 10:17..so we had a few hours to kill...we ate at the airport burgerking aaand me being the wonderful person that i am decided to play HANGMAN! omg...bad idea we played it for like an hour an a half....lololol oh well. i got a few phone calls i saw this sweet kid from another country i wish i woulda asked where he was from..but i'm a chickenshit. well anyway i eventually had the bright idea to buy an newspaper so i had something to do..anybody wanna buy me a minature donkey!??! i was looking in the personals. uuuuhm i played on the escelators(sp.?) for a while..aaaaaand i don't think much else happened..i sat there doing nothing for a while and then stood by the terminal for a while until they came out. oh man i was so exciting waiting there with my camera! don't worry i'll show everybody the pics. wwwwwwwweell there they finally came!!!oh my he is soooo adorable!then we finally got to go home after spending over an hour in there with them...well i didn't get home till 12:30 uhg i was so tired..well now i'm here watching my little sister, probably getting dressed, then going to see the baby, then going to work at 4...exciting day huh? lol well if you read all of that, thanks for you time..i'll talk to you later! <3 *~Andrea~*
